ISIDLULILE emhlabeni indodakazi yowayengumengameli wokuqala omnyama kuleli uDkt Nelson Mandela nowayeyinkosikazi yakhe uNksz Winnie Madikizela-Mandela, uNksz Zindzi Mandela. Izindaba zokushona kukaNkk Mandela (59), obeyinxusa leNingizimu Afrika eDenmark, zivele ngoMsombuluko ekuseni kanti akukacaci ukuthi uthathwe yini kodwa ngokwemibiko kuvela ukuthi ushone ngesonto ebusuku. Udaba lusaqhubeka*